Player is provided with feedback after attempting a task / Q incorrectly
Use when: 
  Player did not complete task correctly
  Standard feedback required 
Features:
  Background: environment
  Q remains visible
  Text includes 
    Confirmation incorrect
    If more than one option, which ones were wrong (but not correct answer)
    Explanatory note
  Confirmation button (forward arrow or similar) to re-try Q
Variables:
  Feedback text
